CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 11, 1952, pg. 16 reads: "Visiting Ministers At AME Conference - An unusual number of visiting ministers and laymen attended the Pittsburgh Annual Conference held last week in Bethel AME Church. Reading left to right, front row; the Revs. G.W. Patterson, J.A. Whitfield, R.H. Reed Jr., C.S. Spivey Sr., Bishop A.J. Allen, who posed with his brethren; N.W. Burton, H.L. Anderson, A.C. Brogdon and Norman W. Browne.  Back row, left to right: The Revs. J.S. Harris, J.D. Jenkins, D.G. Jacobs, W.S.T. Jordon, F.W. Thompson, C.E. Drummer and A.S. King.  Rear: E.W. Jackson and J.C. Burton. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of four clergymen including: Bishop A.J. Allen and N.W. Burton holding envelope, standing in interior for Bethel AME Church annual conference
